{"tid":2174372,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞球迷怒了！街頭豎中指 留下美斯只剩一種可能","createTime":"2020-08-26T00:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T07:47:04.000Z","uid":173952,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c032308fa8fcdc5c86c96c68830396911f77fc8a","tid":2174372,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j6Ytx6q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj6Ytx6q.jpg&h=9bae7f4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/puzDVjL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpuzDVjL.jpg&h=b393e165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1g8k8EM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1g8k8EM.jpg&h=2c8ecf22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n週二，美斯發傳真給巴塞球會，稱已經決定啟動自己的離隊條款，在今年夏天離開魯營。<br />\n<br />\n  消息傳出，巴塞球迷們情緒激動，他們紛紛走上街頭，表示對球會高層的不滿，並發聲支持美斯。<br />\n<br />\n  上百名球迷聚集在魯營球場外，辱罵巴塞主席貝圖美奧以及球會高層，並高呼美斯留下的口號。有人高喊：「貝圖美奧，下台！貝圖美奧，下台！」還有人唱：「美斯請不要走，我們都愛你。」在Twitter上，「美斯yes貝圖美奧No」的話題也在迅速躥紅。<br />\n<br />\n  據加泰羅尼亞媒體分析，目前能讓美斯回心轉意只剩下一種可能，那就是貝圖美奧辭職下台。據悉，巴塞高層將立刻召開緊急會議，商討美斯提出離隊的應對方案，有消息稱，董事成員祖爾迪-莫伊克斯和大衛-比利弗已經提出辭呈，而貝圖美奧在巨大壓力之下，也存在這樣做的可能性。"},{"pid":"fb5139bffbc589cbf9c72531a3187158cbb95ad0","tid":2174372,"uid":2169,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:31:54.000Z","msg":"見到有熱狗"},{"pid":"5c8788edca5f9b84473e01a088f338b04c02ce29","tid":2174372,"uid":173952,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SKETKdx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSKETKdx.jpg&h=2c57bc0a&s={SIZE}\" /> 手足巴塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a806d8cf994bf87c951d56237297537258bc9c3","tid":2174372,"uid":2313,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:32:42.000Z","msg":"巴老母咪同林鄭一